      "rationale": "DePuy Synthes maintains an FDA 21 CFR Part 820-compliant QMS. Ansys solver installation qualification performed per vendor IQ/OQ protocol. All simulation runs executed on locked, version-controlled executables. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2 for medium model risk."
