    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given the prescriptive single-condition nature of ASTM F1717 and consistency with FDA regulatory precedent for spinal fixation submissions. All QoIs satisfy E/uval <1.96 and relative difference <10%. Multi-laboratory, multi-lot, ensemble-model evidence provides high confidence in FEA predictive capability for this COU.",
